About Us

You are the most beautiful girl in the whole world. I fell in love with your smile, your beautiful eyes, and your kind personality. I love how we can change from being goofy to being freaky within a minute and that we can show each other our less charming sides.

From the first moment I saw you, I knew there was something special about you. Our journey together has been filled with unforgettable memories, and every day I discover more reasons to love you. Whether we're sharing laughter, dreams, or even the little moments of silence, my love for you only grows stronger.

Our Story

I remember the "hyggedruk" at Freddie's house, you were wearing your shirt with the kind of glittery blue color, your hair was down, and you were gorgeous. I remember I thought to myself: "she looks perfect". And from that day my feelings for you started growing slowly.
